# GitHub Actions: repo Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → NEWSAPI_KEY
# (Used by scripts/generate-news-pages.js on a schedule to rebuild healthrankings-news.html.)
# Vercel / serverless (optional): api/news.js — never put this key in HTML.
#
# NewsAPI “Developer” keys work for server-side CI; if the job logs HTTP 401/426 or
# “userAgent not allowed”, upgrade the key or check https://newsapi.org/pricing
NEWSAPI_KEY=

# Optional: extra comma-separated origins allowed to call api/news.js (browser Origin / Referer).
# Defaults already include https://healthrankings.co, www, Render URL, and local dev ports.
# ALLOWED_API_ORIGINS=https://preview.example.com
